se.ltu.android.demo.scene.animation
Class KeyFrameAnimation

java.lang.Object
  se.ltu.android.demo.scene.animation.KeyFrameAnimation

public class KeyFrameAnimation
extends java.lang.Object

A key frame-based animation path. A key frame is nothing more than a transformation and a point in time. Any spatial affected by this animation will move between the set transformation at the specified moments in time.

Note: currently it only support translations. While implementing scaling is easy, the scene should support quaternions to effectively interpolate the rotation between two key frames.
